text:
I see two approaches to write programs.
I start entirely on the green meadow, or I'm looking for a template.

I want to go this way:
For example, I design the surface with a tool we mdbootstrap.

<https://mdbootstrap.com/education/bootstrap/quick-start/>

Then I try to simplify the code using HARBOURINO.
Then I fill the web page with data then come from DBF files.
It should be quick that you can fill a template with data and personalize the web page.

elements.text:
I see two approaches to write programs.
I start entirely on the green meadow, or I'm looking for a template.

I want to go this way:
For example, I design the surface with a tool we mdbootstrap.

Then I try to simplify the code using HARBOURINO.
Then I fill the web page with data then come from DBF files.
It should be quick that you can fill a template with data and personalize the web page.
